companies.title: PIH Engage Co-Leader
companies.description: Organize fundraising events for Partners In Health to reach chapter's donation goal of $1000, host monthly meetings to educate students about the health issues that Partners in Health targets, exercise political efficacy by meeting with legislatures to push for changes in budget vital to Partners in Health's efforts, and attend PIH Engage leader meetings to stay informed with the movements Partners in Health is implementing.

companies.title: Chapter President
